### Get a recent record (less than 3 months old)
GET http://<your-container-app-url>/records/hot-record-123
Content-Type: application/json

### Get an old, archived record (older than 3 months)
# This call should hit the retrieval function
GET http://<your-container-app-url>/records/cold-record-456
Content-Type: application/json

### Get a record that does not exist
GET http://<your-container-app-url>/records/non-existent-record
Content-Type: application/json
